CREATE VIEW [dbo].[f_planning_book]



	AS 
	
	SELECT [forecast_snapshot] as [Version	Date],	
	       Null                as [Date],
		   Null					  [IdProduct],	
	       Null                   [Ex-Factory],	
		   Null                   [Sales to pharmacies],	
		   Null                       [Open Stock],	
		   Null                       [Close Stock],	
		   Null                       [Open Stock Pharmacies],	
		   Null                       [Close Stock Pharmacies],
		   Null                       [Free Goods Promo Adjustment],
		   Null                       [Consumer Off Take],	
		   Null                       [IDCountry],	



	
	FROM f_planning_book
